<br>
Sow &gt; jboots surprisingly enough.<br>
Bow range &gt; DD range.<br>
Track actually works again.<br>
<br>
Course, in this fight, I could have gated whenever I wanted. But could I have won? Dispells are very important, and Uin was dispelling my levi so I didn't stand much chance using that to advantage.<br>
<br>
Sure if you get ganked at a portal by 2 wiz chances are you will die. Is that a reason to nerf wizards tho? So that the ONLY way wizards can kill people is by finding 4 other wizards and ganking people at portals? Bad idea imo, it's bad enough as it is.<br>
<br>
